{"word":"μάρτυς","slug":"μάρτυς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μάρτυς, μάρτυρος, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>μεριμνᾶω</el> ‘care for’] ‘one who attests the fact or truth of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, <b>witness<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in legal context <b><a href='B:470 18:16'>Mt 18:16</a>; <a href='B:470 26:65'>26:65</a>; <a href='B:510 6:13'>Ac 6:13</a>; <a href='B:510 7:58'>7:58</a>; <a href='B:540 13:1'>2 Cor 13:1</a>; <a href='B:610 5:19'>1 Ti 5:19</a>; <a href='B:650 10:28'>Hb 10:28</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense of anyone who attests or corroborates<b> <a href='B:490 11:48'>Lk 11:48</a>; <a href='B:490 24:48'>24:48</a>; <a href='B:510 1:8'>Ac 1:8</a>; <a href='B:520 1:9'>Ro 1:9</a>; <a href='B:540 1:23'>2 Cor 1:23</a>; <a href='B:570 1:8'>Phil 1:8</a>; <a href='B:590 2:10'>1 Th 2:10</a>; <a href='B:610 6:12'>1 Ti 6:12</a>; <a href='B:620 2:2'>2 Ti 2:2</a>; <a href='B:650 12:1'>Hb 12:1</a>; <a href='B:670 5:1'>1 Pt 5:1</a>;</b> at cost of one’s life, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> rendered as martyr, but in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> the focus is on the role of witness <b><a href='B:510 22:20'>Ac 22:20</a>; <a href='B:730 1:5'>Rv 1:5</a>; <a href='B:730 2:13'>2:13</a>; <a href='B:730 3:14'>3:14</a>; <a href='B:730 17:6'>17:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μαρτύρομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μασάομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}